Sniper


Sniper sees Anubis and Hades leap into the air. Sniper pulls out his 
rocket launcher and fires 1 Rocket at Hades. He then throws down the 
Launcher and fires 40 lasers from his 2 rifle,on rapid blast, and 3 
optic Blast at Anubis.



 Anubis and Hades leapt into the air.  Anubis transformed into a left 
arm, 
 going into the air, while Hades turned into a leg, a left leg, 
heading into 
 the air.
